text: Hybolasius laticollis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Broun in 1903. It is known from New Zealand.BioLib.cz - Hybolasius laticollis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1903
